data.description: Welcome to fabulous! Newly updated extended Capri villa offer 2 bedrooms, 2 baths plus den and a 2 car garage. The soaring vaulted ceilings allow for a grand spacious living experience. Upgrades include new Interior & exterior paint, new lighting throughout the home, new exterior painting, landscaping /  lighting and new whole house hurricane shutters.  The new expansive outdoor lanai  is perfect for family entertaining., grilling or relaxing in the brand new hot tub. There is beautiful quartz in the kitchen with custom backsplash ( Ohio State Buckeyes Fans) and custom  6"quartz  in bathrooms.  Bedrooms have high end LPV flooring and all showers have new 1/2' glass doors.  Roof 5 years old - AC 3 years old. Fees include cable, hi-speed internet & lawn maintenance. Two pools, har-tru tennis courts, pickle ball and bocce courts, fitness center, putting green, hair & nail salon, restaurant, gas station & post office are all part of the town center enjoyed by all. Four miles of sidewalk around the lakes with wildlife galore! This location offers A rated schools, new restaurants & medical facilities nearby. A short 8 minute drive to Mercato, Seed to Table and the popular Vanderbilt Beach.
